<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>2 SPEED AND DOUBLE REDUCTION SINGLE DRIVE AXLES: EATON - ADJUST/INSTALL - DIFFERENTIAL CARRIER FINAL
        ASSEMBLY
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
        <title>DIFFERENTIAL CARRIER FINAL ASSEMBLY</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install adjuster lock and bolt on ring gear teeth side.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">2-Speed Axles (on backface side of ring gear): Install adjuster lock, dowel bushings and
                bolts. Tighten bolts (refer to the ,
                <hotlnk document="s14016_HL1401602.xml" xrefid="hl1401602">TORQUE CHART</hotlnk>). Lockwire differential
                bearing cap, and adjuster lock bolts.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">2-Speed Axles: Position shift fork in carrier opening, then install sliding clutch. With
                clutch installed, engage shift fork yoke with clutch collar. Then install shift fork shaft. Install
                expansion plugs to seal openings. Install shift unit seal and spring (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1401652">Figure 52</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1401652" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1401652" filename="../figg14/g1401652.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 52. Differential Carrier Final Assembly</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Planetary Double Reduction Axles (on backface side of ring gear): Install sun gear, retainer
                and bolts that fasten both retainer and adjuster lock (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1401653">Figure 53</hotlnk>). Tighten bolts (refer to the ,
                <hotlnk document="s14016_HL1401602.xml" xrefid="hl1401602">TORQUE CHART</hotlnk>) and lockwire.
            </para>
            <figure id="f1401653" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1401653" filename="../figg14/g1401653.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 53. Sun Gear Components</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
